Author: CycloShieldCoin
Title: CycloShieldCoin, Real time road data collection token
Body: CycloShieldCoin ‚ÄúReal time road data collection token‚Äù   Our token is primed to be the real time road data collection token: everything happening on the road such as dangerous spots, speeds, traffic, reckless drivers, etc . Bicycles and motorbikes acting as data collection agents, rewarding users for their participation and preparing this data for big data analysis and consumption is s revolutionary idea  Jaguar is considering rewarding users for real time road data collection, good to see we were the pioneers. Car manufacturers or any other company willing to join our technology are welcome to use our interoperable API  And we have built a gadget for Cyclists, CycloShield Nano which already exists and it's getting ready for production   Web: https://www.cycloshieldcoin.com/  Our platform CycloShield, presented on Kickstarter last summer, is an advanced safety system for cyclists. CycloShieldCoin, one of our latest breakthroughs, will let us reward cyclists every time they share information about the state of the roads, blackspots, and safe routes.  Part of our business model is selling Ads on our App. Advertisers will want to reach our high purchasing power audience and we offer then an attractive platform for which they'll have to pay using CYS.  However, Cryptocurrencies are not always easy to use for the less tech-savvy or they have to go through many hoops to acquire them. We acknowledge this fact and have devised a way to reduce friction and bring more Corporate users on board: a Online Token Store to our CYS token.   Additional measures such as token burning will help the market sustain the price and have enough liquidity for a healthy economy. Our strategy of burning part of the tokens we receive will gradually reduce the token supply and might cause the token to increase in value due to an ever decreasing token supply.     Whitepaper: https://drive.google.com/file/d/0BxhuNRihFKvsTW9wS3BDVXRPSWc/view?usp=sharing  Video Interviews: Coin Interview:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oj4i6jT0Oik  Product repos:  Token Contract:https://github.com/cycloshield/tokencontract App: https://github.com/cycloshield/cycloshieldnano-app  Find us online and connect:  Telegram: https://t.me/CycloShieldCoin Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/CycloShield Twitter: https://twitter.com/CycloShield Medium: https://medium.com/@CycloShieldCoin
